{"tid":2348742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"党鐵：延續八達通八折優惠至明(2021)年3月底","createTime":"2021-01-01T03:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T04:15:07.000Z","uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2a3c77a669d1f722af86b1ecd9e9ccdef7bf07","tid":2348742,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"港鐵今日（23日）宣布，將原定明年1月1日結束的八達通「程程20%車費扣減」延續至明年3月31日，優惠適用於使用八達通的所有港鐵乘客以及於2021年1月23日起使用車票二維碼乘搭重鐵的乘客。<br />\n<br />\n 與此同時，乘客購買2021年1月至6月的「全月通加強版」以及在2021年6月30日或之前購買「港鐵都會票」，亦可繼續享有100元扣減。<br />\n<br />\n 至於早前公布調整售價的「全月通加強版」及「港鐵都會票」，新售價將會在明年7月才生效。乘客可於12月25日(星期五)起，繼續以優惠價在車站購買明年一月份的「全月通加強版」，另外更可透過MTR Mobile自行購買「全月通加強版」車票，減省前往車站排隊購票的時間。<br />\n<br />\n 港鐵指，乘客亦可以繼續享有2020/21年度其他車費推廣計劃，及為不同層面的乘客群提供的恆常優惠。"},{"pid":"ff8da7aa1b83d07edc7f1d43e3e0e1d3cd677d8d","tid":2348742,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:52:41.000Z","msg":"香港商報網 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔貼lnk"},{"pid":"fb1ad6eb536a38d0ea3c3be798da1913bb7668f8","tid":2348742,"uid":76793,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"晨咁早搭 個個8折？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d5a1332dd70a6a8d8a63f6fa0aaf7eb6abd576","tid":2348742,"uid":159074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"2蚊折<br />\n直到你搞實名為止"},{"pid":"d94a8adae7b06e625309eccd9e70b144e9d3a0f9","tid":2348742,"uid":341040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"1.6正呀<br />\n<br />\n利申：65碎"},{"pid":"db93cbb3e20732398bfa266730e53de104b7af16","tid":2348742,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:08:44.000Z"